snippet.title: Nintendo presents: New Style Boutique 3 – Styling Star - Launch Trailer (Nintendo 3DS)
snippet.description:
Style the stars of tomorrow in Nintendo presents: New Style Boutique 3 – Styling Star!

Get the free demo from Nintendo eShop on your Nintendo 3DS family system, or from the official website!
